| transmission = 3-speed ''[[Ford ATX transmission|ATX]]'' [[automatic transmission|automatic]]<br />4-speed ''[[Ford AXOD transmission|AXOD]]'' [[automatic transmission|automatic]]<br />4-speed ''[[Ford AXOD-E transmission|AXOD-E]]'' [[automatic transmission|automatic]]<br />5-speed ''[[Ford MTX transmission|MTX]]'' [[manual transmission|manual]]<br />5-speed ''[[Ford MTX transmission#MTX-IV|MTX-IV]]'' [[manual transmission|manual]]
